Day-02

### linux version explain

X -> major update
X -> minor update, even : Stable, odd : test
X -> release, patch
x.x.x-u10
x.x.x-p10
x.x.x-fc23r10

### Install openssh-server

> apt -y install openssh-server
> 

### systemctl status ssh

> ufw allow ssh
> 

> nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config
33 PermitRootLogin yes
^x -> y -> <Enter>
> 

> service ssh restart
> 

